message: Hi Bob! I have a fantastic product available that I think you would really benefit from. I'm offering it to you at a price of $15000.
Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. I'm interested in your product, but I'm looking to keep my expenses considerably lower. I'd be willing to purchase it for $12000. Let me know if that works for you.
I appreciate your interest, Bob! While I understand your budget constraints, I can't go as low as $12000. How about $14000? I believe this product offers tremendous value.
